---
title: Char Siu Pork Meatball & Noodle Bowl with Spinach & Crispy Shallots
description: Introducing the ultimate solution to the classic dilemma; when you can’t decide between two superstar dishes. Meatballs or noodles, we say let’s have both! The decadent char siu sauce will soak into the meatballs and the noodles do nicely to add a little extra texture and tastiness. You won’t ever have to compromise again.
